==Notes==
'''a.''' {{Note_label|a|a|none}} The year of Koniecpolski's birth is not certain since there are several conflicting sources. [[Leszek Podhorodecki]], in his biography ''Stanis<U+0142>aw Koniecpolski ok. 1592<U+2013>1646'', chose the date 1592, which is likely the "average" of other sources (1590 being the earliest, 1594 the latest given by various sources).{{Citation needed|date=August 2009}} As he notes, the date 1591 is the most common ([http://www.britannica.com/eb/article-9046002/Stanislaw-Koniecpolski used] for example by [[Encyclop<U+00E6>dia Britannica]], 7 August 2007), and the date 1593 or 1594 was proposed in [[Polski S<U+0142>ownik Biograficzny]] by historian  [[W<U+0142>adys<U+0142>aw Czapli<U+0144>ski]], whom Podhorodecki calls 'a great specialist of that era', noting however that Czapli<U+0144>ski fails to justify this date.{{Citation needed|date=August 2009}}

